  "headline": "<h2>A Rainbow of Crystals to Brighten Your Day: Symbol Design and Value</h2>",
  "content": "<p>Kluster Krystals Megaclusters is a treat for the eyes, with sparkling crystals of blue, red, purple, pink, and green. It's like a Justin Bieber concert for your retinas! And if that isn't enough, up to 100 symbols can appear on the screen at once - that's more crystals than your great aunt's collection. Plus, with the red crystal being the highest-paying symbol, you could win up to 50 times your bet and be the envy of all your friends. But wait, there's more! Some symbols may appear in larger sizes and come equipped with multipliers of x1, x2, x3, x4, x5, and even x10! With these crystals, you'll feel like you're walking on sunshine and soaring like an eagle.</p>"
